text: Female Staff was so rude. She was using the phone blatantly in front of me and I had to say excuse me many times. Even afterwards, I was glared at and then begrudgingly served.

Bought 2 original doughnuts and they were packed into 2 paper bags. As I was heading for fairprice,  I asked if I could have a carrier, the cashier said 20 cents and she further explained that the bag was big. The assistant behind her was laughing out loud( in front of the customer?)
What a service.

I know it’s centralize kitchen for their donuts but so far I only buy from this branch which is near my place. So I will say it’s soft and delicious. Super addictive. You will love it if you are a sweet tooth person.
